txt.en: There is much to be done in the Haradrim encampment of Dûm Boha.
Enter the enemy encampment of Dûm Boha
The Haradrim encampment seems well stocked, with provisions littered throughout. Perhaps destroying some will cut at their strength and sow discord.
The Haradrim encampment of Dûm Boha is located on the western slopes of the Slag-hills.\n\nYou should destroy Haradrim supplies stored around the encampment.
